REMEMBER: Add a player to your face list

Syntax: remember <player>

DESCRIPTION:
  Adds a player to your recognized list so you see their name instead of
  their race description in room text. This is one-way recognition.

NOTES:
  Use introduce for mutual recognition.
  The target may be in the room or online anywhere.
  Use forget to remove someone from your list.

SEE ALSO: known, forget, introduce
